name: JokesGalore
0:
”Alexa, open Jokes Galore”
”Alexa, ask Jokes Galore tell me a joke”
”Alexa, ask Jokes Galore say a joke”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: jokes galore
des: The skill was built to provide Amazon Echo users with jokes that they might have heard of but haven't heard or have forgotten. As an added bonus I've included jokes of my own. Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
